comments: Caruso (CHI) cleanly deflects the ball as simultaneous marginal contact occurs with Monk's (SAC) right side during the pass attempt.
Dosunmu (CHI) is shuffling alongside Fox's (SAC) path, and marginal body contact occurs as they come together near the wing.
Dosunmu (CHI) is drawn into the air on the pump fake toward Fox (SAC) and initiates body/arm contact that affects Fox's SQBR.
Barnes (SAC) is turning slightly when marginal body contact occurs with DeRozan (CHI) after DeRozan's gather.
Monk's (SAC) fingertips graze Vucevic's (CHI) left arm, and marginal contact occurs during Vucevic's put-back attempt.
Vucevic (CHI) makes contact with the ball after it exits the imaginary cylinder above the rim.
Caruso (CHI) slides his hand off Fox's (SAC) right arm as Fox dribbles over the pick and passes.
DeRozan (CHI) is moving somewhat laterally when he and Barnes (SAC) come together at the end of the drive.
Caruso (CHI) establishes himself in Barnes' (SAC) path and does not deliver illegal contact as he sets the pick.
Fox (SAC) slightly extends forward prior to marginal body contact occurring with DeRozan (CHI) in the lane.
Caruso (CHI) and Fox (SAC) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.
Caruso (CHI) has his hands brought forward when marginal contact occurs with Monk's (SAC) midsection as Monk changes direction during the drive.
Caruso (CHI) and Vucevic (CHI) each legally contest Monk's (SAC) driving shot attempt.

Caruso (CHI) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds. After communicating with the Replay Center, it was determined that Monk's (SAC) preceding shot attempt made contact with the rim and the shot clock was reset to 14 seconds.
Caruso (CHI) initiates contact with Fox's (SAC) face as Fox receives the pass.
Caruso (CHI) establishes himself in Barnes' (SAC) path and does not deliver illegal contact during the pick.
Fox (SAC) makes contact with the ball as simultaneous marginal contact occurs with DeRozan's (CHI) slightly extended off-arm after DeRozan's gather.

Sabonis (SAC) collapses his left forearm to his front as he absorbs the initial marginal contact with DeRozan (CHI). He then raises his right arm into a vertical position prior to further incidental contact occurring during DeRozan's driving shot attempt.
Caruso (CHI) commits a take foul on Monk (SAC). The transition take foul rule does not apply to the last two minutes of either the fourth quarter or overtime.
Sabonis (SAC) maintains verticality and incidental body contact occurs with White (CHI) after White releases the pass.
Fox (SAC) legally contests Vucevic's (CHI) jump shot attempt.
Caruso (CHI) and Dosunmu (CHI) make incidental contact with Monk (SAC) as they each raise an arm in pursuit of the rebound.
Caruso's (CHI) leg touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.
White (CHI) commits a take foul on Barnes (SAC).
